            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your<strong> vegetable stock mix </strong>in 750ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [950ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.4L] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> and add your <strong>saffron</strong> – this is your <strong>saffron stock</strong></p><p>Once the garlic is fragrant, add your <strong>arborio rice</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min, stirring to coat the grains in the oil</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1591624629632-x200.jpg",
