            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the risotto is cooked, add your <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong>, most of your <strong>grated Italian hard cheese </strong>(save some for garnish!) and your <strong>clotted cream</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 1 min or until the cheese has melted – this is your <strong>creamy</strong> <strong>saffron risotto</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
