    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>rested steak</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>creamy saffron risotto</strong> and sprinkle over the <strong>remaining grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>sliced steak</strong> and serve the <strong>balsamic salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
